column2: SELECT      s.specObjID   s.ra, s.dec       into MyDB.hst_qsos from MyDB.hst_gz AS m   OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjAllEq( m.RA, m.DEC, #) AS n   LEFT JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON n.specObjID = s.specObjID   LEFT JOIN PhotoObjAll AS p ON n.specObjID = p.specObjID   LEFT JOIN galSpecExtra e ON n.specObjID = e.specObjID   WHERE   e.bptclass = # AND   s.z <= #
